<subSubSection id="C6878F804629FFE2FF4FFDFAFE80FD00" pageId="4" pageNumber="49" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8E22DC0B4629FFE2FF4FFDFAFE80FD00" blockId="4.[136,1452,530,736]" pageId="4" pageNumber="49">
<emphasis id="BCE900194629FFE2FF4FFDFAFF67FDCC" bold="true" box="[136,201,530,556]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="49">Notes</emphasis>
:—Vieira (1988) recognized three subspecies for 
<taxonomicName id="499DA7884629FFE2FCD2FDFAFC5CFDCC" box="[789,1010,530,556]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Campanulaceae" genus="Lobelia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="4" pageNumber="49" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="organensis">
<emphasis id="BCE900194629FFE2FCD2FDFAFC5CFDCC" box="[789,1010,530,556]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="49">Lobelia organensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
based on morphological variation in trichomes, dimensions of the floral structures, and geographic distribution. Her proposal, however, could not be considered validly published, as it was part of her unpublished MSc thesis. The collection 
<emphasis id="BCE900194629FFE2FB65FDB3FA0AFD94" box="[1186,1444,602,628]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="49">Prance &amp; Silva 59034</emphasis>
, assigned to the invalidly published 
<taxonomicName id="499DA7884629FFE2FDDCFD97FC23FD78" box="[539,909,638,664]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Campanulaceae" genus="Lobelia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="4" pageNumber="49" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="subSpecies" species="organensis" subSpecies="brasiliensis">
<emphasis id="BCE900194629FFE2FDDCFD97FD1AFD78" box="[539,692,639,664]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="49">L. organensis</emphasis>
subsp. 
<emphasis id="BCE900194629FFE2FCCBFD96FC23FD78" box="[780,909,638,664]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="49">brasiliensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Vieira 1988), was later used as the 
<typeStatus id="512662A94629FFE2FAF6FD96FACFFD78" box="[1329,1377,638,664]" pageId="4" pageNumber="49">type</typeStatus>
of the newly described species 
<taxonomicName id="499DA7884629FFE2FE64FD4BFDEDFD5C" box="[419,579,674,700]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Campanulaceae" genus="Lobelia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="4" pageNumber="49" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="brasiliensis">
<emphasis id="BCE900194629FFE2FE64FD4BFDEDFD5C" box="[419,579,674,700]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="49">L. brasiliensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(
<bibRefCitation id="EA0CA1FA4629FFE2FD94FD4AFCC1FD5C" author="Vieira, A. O. S. &amp; Shepherd, G. J." box="[595,879,674,700]" firstAuthor="Vieira" journalOrPublisher="Novon" pageId="4" pageNumber="49" pagination="457 - 460" part="8" refId="ref8361" refString="Vieira, A. O. S. &amp; Shepherd, G. J. (1998) A new species of Lobelia (Campanulaceae) from Brazil. Novon 8 (4): 457 - 460. https: // doi. org / 10.2307 / 3391874" title="A new species of Lobelia (Campanulaceae) from Brazil" type="journal article" year="1998">Vieira &amp; Shepherd 1998</bibRefCitation>
). The isotype cited as kept at M in the protologue was not found.
</paragraph>
